New Features and Important Changes in ctools 1.3.1

27 June 2017


Introduction
------------
This document briefly summarizes the changes that have been made in this
ctools release with respect to the precedent release.


Configuration
-------------
None


Python interface
----------------
None


Support model
-------------
None


ctobssim - CTA observation simulation
-------------------------------------
The working log file pointer is now correctly forwarded to
ctobssim::set_mc_id_names() which avoids exceptions when running the
tool under OpenMP (#2123).


