cscripts
--------
The csobsselect script now accepts an observation container upon construction.

The standard deviation computation in cssrcdetect has been corrected.

The csroot2caldb script now uses the MigMatrixNoTheta2cut_offaxis and
AngularPSF2DEtrue_offaxis ROOT histograms to compute the energy dispersion matrix
and the PSF shape (#2135).


